						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the <hi rend="italic">chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>Vīra-Ballāḷa II.</p>						

						<p>The partially preserved details of the date in this damaged record are Śaka 1 • • •, Mārgaśira-puṇṇami.</p>						

						<p>It records a grant of land and house-site by Beḷḷaḷa Nāga-gāvuṇḍa, for a feeding house <hi rend="italic">(satra)</hi> at Baḷaganūru. The gift was entrusted to the ascetic Chandrabhūshaṇa-yati, whose virtues are extolled at length. </p>						

						</summary>
